Last week, we had the honor of hosting @freddsters Austin stop on his tour for his NEW cookbook, Let’s Make It! 📖❤️

We had a blast enjoying a cooking demo and delicious food straight from the pages of Let’s Make It. It’s always the best time coming together for events like this one to celebrate our extended familia members and their milestones, connect with community, and make amazing memories together! Juntos es Mejor. 🥰
